OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FThis morning will be cloudy
OL,6,Fwith spells of rain although drier
OL,7,Ftowards the east coast. This afternoon
OL,8,Fwill see some dry weather with a few
OL,9,Fshowers. Some brightness possible
OL,10,Falong the east coast.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FThis evening will see a few
OL,13,Fshowers. The rest of the night will
OL,14,Fsee variable amounts of cloud with
OL,15,Ffurther showers or longer spells of
OL,16,Frain.
OL,17,
OL,18,CSaturday:FAny overnight showers soon
OL,19,Fdying out. Then the rest of the day
OL,20,Fwill be dry with sunny spells.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
