OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FDry,
OL,6,Fbright and warm on Sunday. Mainly dry,
OL,7,Fbright and very warm on Monday,
OL,8,Fperhaps the odd shower. Clouider on
OL,9,FTuesday with the odd shower.
